lyrics:
[Verse]
In this moment, I'll seize the day
Carpe diem, no time to delay
Every second counts, gotta make it right
Life's a canvas, gonna paint it bright

[Chorus]
Live life to the fullest, while I'm alive
Every heartbeat, a chance to thrive
No promises for the next breath I'll take
Gonna shine like the stars, no time to break
